<mvc:View height="100%" controllerName="vatmanui5.webApp.view.Login" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc">
    <App id="app" backgroundImage="" >
        <Page id="__page0" enableScrolling="false" floatingFooter="false" >
            <content>
                <FlexBox width="100%" id="__box0" alignItems="End" justifyContent="End" >

	                        <items>
								<HBox>
								<Image
									src="../images/logo_with_text_t.png"
									densityAware="false"
										decorative="true"
									width="{/imageWidth}" 
									height="4em">
									<layoutData>
										<FlexItemData growFactor="1" />
									</layoutData>
								</Image>
							</HBox>
	                        </items>

	                    </FlexBox>
                <FlexBox height="100%" alignItems="Center" justifyContent="Center">
                    <items>
                        <VBox>
                            <Input id="userId" placeholder="Enter user ..." />
                            <Input id="pw" type="Password" placeholder="Enter password ..."/>
                            <Button text="Login" press="login"/>
                        </VBox>
                    </items>
                </FlexBox>
            </content>
            <footer>
                <Toolbar width="100%" id="__toolbar3">
                    <content></content>
                </Toolbar>
            </footer>
        </Page>
    </App>
</mvc:View>